programme.title: Africas Claws Jaws 1 #4

programme.title: 野性之最紐西蘭 #5

programme.title: 「非」常爪牙 #2
programme.desc: 蛇、蜘蛛和蠍子是令很多人聞風喪膽的爬行生物。然而在非洲,這些物種卻是身經百戰的頂級獵食者。窺探這些有毒生物的捕獵方法、特殊技能和神祕的愛情生活。

programme.title: Africas Claws Jaws 1 #2
programme.desc: Snakes, spiders, and scorpions are the kind of creepy crawlies many fear the most. But in Africa, these species are refined predators. Explore the hunting methods, special skills, and secret love lives of these venomous creatures.

programme.title: 「非」常爪牙 #4
programme.desc: 非洲 - 一個充滿生機的大陸。它的動物貴族是最為人熟悉,潛伏在陰影中的各式各樣爬行類。牠們征服了所有棲息地,並進化出一系列非凡的適應性,成為地下世界無容置疑的主人。

programme.title: Africas Claws Jaws 1 #4
programme.desc: Africa - a continent teeming with life. While its animal aristocrats are the most familiar, lurking in the shadows is a diversity of reptiles. They’ve conquered just about every habitat and have evolved a remarkable array of adaptations that make them the undisputed masters of the underworld.

programme.title: 野性之最紐西蘭 #5
programme.desc: 紐西蘭與世隔絕的島嶼是不凡的天堂及家園,以擁有多元又獨特的野生動物聞名。尤以不會飛的鳥類、古代爬行類和沿海哺乳類最為人所共知,仔細觀察將會發現另一個世界。這裡有微型的怪物、小型的掠奪者和微小的恐怖,卻帶來了非凡的生命。每個獵人也是獵物﹐永遠需要努力生存。走進灌木叢,又會發現不同規模的生活。從巨型肉食蜈蚣和夜行蟋蟀到捕魚蛛和使用絲質陷阱的發光蠕蟲。奇怪而奇妙,這些無名英雄是野性紐西蘭最令人毛骨悚然的爬行類。

programme.title: Wildest New Zealand 1 #5
programme.desc: New Zealand’s isolated islands are famed as an unusual paradise, home to a variety of unique wildlife. Best known for its flightless birds, ancient reptiles and coastal mammals, a closer look reveals another world. A land of miniature monsters, Lilliputian predators and tiny terrors that lead remarkable lives, where every hunter is also the hunted and survival is always a giant struggle. Journey into the undergrowth and discover life on a different scale. From giant carnivorous centipedes and nocturnal crickets to fishing spiders and glowing worms with silken traps. Weird and wonderful, these unsung heroes are Wildest New Zealand’s Creepiest Crawlies.

programme.title: 美國在野四季錄 #3

programme.title: Americas Wild Seasons 1 #3
